The Crew PC Gameplay | The Crew 4K Gameplay | The Crew PC Walkthrough | PC 4K 60FPS |

The Crew is an open-world action-driving racing game developed by Ivory Tower and Ubisoft Reflections and published by Ubisoft for Microsoft Windows, PlayStation 4 and Xbox One, with an Xbox 360 port developed by Asobo Studio. The first expansion, titled The Crew: Wild Run, was released on November 17, 2015. The second expansion, entitled The Crew: Calling All Units, was released on November 29, 2016. And a sequel, The Crew 2, was released worldwide on June 29, 2018.
